actions.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.

official_title: To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to repeal the increase in tax on fuel used in commercial aviation which is scheduled to take effect on October 1, 1995.
short_title: Commercial Aviation Fuel Tax Repeal Act of 1995

summary.text: Commercial Aviation Fuel Tax Repeal Act of 1995 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to repeal the increase in tax on fuel used in commercial aviation scheduled to take effect after September 30, 1995.

titles.title: Commercial Aviation Fuel Tax Repeal Act of 1995
To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to repeal the increase in tax on fuel used in commercial aviation which is scheduled to take effect on October 1, 1995.
